WEBVTT

00:00:34.470 --> 00:00:35.950 line:80%
It smells so good.

00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:37.360 line:80%
What's cooking?

00:00:38.440 --> 00:00:40.040 line:80%
I'd really like to have some.

00:00:51.830 --> 00:00:53.320 line:80%
My sister is making
a tasty braised dish again.

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.120 line:80%
What is it?

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:55.250 line:80%
I'm not telling you.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:05.660 line:80%
Changning,

00:01:05.870 --> 00:01:08.000 line:80%
tell Mrs. Zhao not to make dinner.

00:01:08.440 --> 00:01:11.040 line:80%
We'll send them noodles
with pork intestines.

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:13.220 line:80%
Go do it now.

00:01:26.670 --> 00:01:28.400 line:80%
You little glutton. Off you go.

00:01:31.870 --> 00:01:33.480 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao,

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:36.600 line:80%
my sister says
you don't need to make dinner today,

00:01:36.839 --> 00:01:40.360 line:80%
since she'll cook noodles
with pork intestines for you.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:13.080 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:03:13.170 --> 00:03:15.740 line:80%
[Episode 2]

00:03:17.879 --> 00:03:19.390 line:80%
Dinner's ready!

00:03:24.550 --> 00:03:26.160 line:80%
Mr. Zhao made you a crutch.

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:28.990 line:80%
Thanks.

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:47.080 line:80%
No pig's tail at all.

00:03:47.510 --> 00:03:49.110 line:80%
We're having "meat gourds" today.

00:03:49.110 --> 00:03:51.040 line:80%
I'll braise a pig's tail tomorrow.

00:03:57.950 --> 00:03:59.750 line:80%
Have you forgotten Mom's rules?

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:02.580 line:80%
Don't be rude.
We can't eat until the guest does.

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:06.510 line:80%
We'll eat after you, sir.

00:04:07.230 --> 00:04:07.910 line:80%
Thanks.

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:39.480 line:80%
You've been having porridge these days.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.540 line:80%
Is one bowl of noodles enough for you?

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:44.250 line:80%
O-One bowl of noodles is...

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:45.320 line:80%
enough...

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:46.360 line:80%
You're in recovery.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.490 line:80%
You should eat more.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.280 line:80%
Yes, eat more.

00:04:54.630 --> 00:04:55.280 line:80%
Thank you.

00:05:03.070 --> 00:05:03.720 line:80%
Is it good?

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:06.700 line:80%
Yes, very good.

00:05:08.070 --> 00:05:09.360 line:80%
What exactly...

00:05:09.430 --> 00:05:10.490 line:80%
are "meat gourds"?

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:11.570 line:80%
Intestines.

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.630 line:80%
Pork intestines.

00:05:17.070 --> 00:05:19.200 line:80%
I was worried you wouldn't like offal.

00:05:19.430 --> 00:05:21.750 line:80%
Seeing how much you enjoy it
has put my mind at ease.

00:05:21.750 --> 00:05:22.520 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.780 line:80%
I already got all the pig feces out...

00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:28.050 line:80%
I mean...

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.360 line:80%
I cleaned the intestines thoroughly.

00:05:31.360 --> 00:05:34.430 line:80%
Mr. Zhao likes those
that have only been washed once,

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:36.980 line:80%
saying that feces give them more flavor.

00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:41.430 line:80%
You scared me!

00:05:42.870 --> 00:05:43.750 line:80%
What now?

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:46.520 line:80%
Do I even need to report to you
before I sneeze?

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:47.550 line:80%
But you gave me a fright!

00:05:47.550 --> 00:05:49.080 line:80%
Could I have controlled it?

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.490 line:80%
Are you done eating?

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:54.000 line:80%
There's so much left.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:57.070 line:80%
A few bites are already enough

00:05:57.070 --> 00:05:58.230 line:80%
for me since I'm weak now.

00:05:58.230 --> 00:05:59.070 line:80%
Are you sure?

00:05:59.430 --> 00:06:00.280 line:80%
Yes, I'm sure.

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:02.630 line:80%
Had better not to waste it.

00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:03.840 line:80%
Food is precious.

00:06:06.280 --> 00:06:06.840 line:80%
Eat up.

00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:14.720 line:80%
Is this...

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:16.670 line:80%
what you usually eat?

00:06:17.230 --> 00:06:19.160 line:80%
We don't get to have this every day.

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:22.360 line:80%
Only when the New Year is approaching

00:06:22.360 --> 00:06:23.990 line:80%
and people start butchering pigs

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:26.190 line:80%
would they give Changyu some offal.

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:31.210 line:80%
It's been a long time since I last had
noodles with pork intestines.

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.300 line:80%
Thank you for the noodles.

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:39.190 line:80%
A pig's tail will be served tomorrow,

00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:41.050 line:80%
since Changyu will butcher a pig.

00:06:43.990 --> 00:06:45.920 line:80%
-You know how to butcher pigs?
-No.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.190 line:80%
How is it possible
for a delicate and sweet girl

00:06:50.190 --> 00:06:51.920 line:80%
such as myself to butcher pigs?

00:06:52.110 --> 00:06:53.910 line:80%
My sister was running her mouth.

00:06:55.310 --> 00:06:56.310 line:80%
Don't believe it.

00:07:11.430 --> 00:07:13.190 line:80%
You stay here. Keep quiet.

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:23.930 line:80%
Changning, come here.

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:26.050 line:80%
Let's play hide-and-seek.

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:30.360 line:80%
Open the door!

00:07:30.920 --> 00:07:31.950 line:80%
Open up!

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.670 line:80%
She's a pig butcher.

00:08:09.190 --> 00:08:10.670 line:80%
You were a good pig in this life.

00:08:10.670 --> 00:08:12.470 line:80%
Be a good person in the next life!

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:21.580 line:80%
I'll feed you by butchering pigs!

00:08:31.910 --> 00:08:34.430 line:80%
Changning, time to wash your face!

00:08:38.950 --> 00:08:39.550 line:80%
Come on.

00:08:45.350 --> 00:08:47.950 line:80%
Changyu, where is your silver hairpin?

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:49.280 line:80%
I pawned it.

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:51.800 line:80%
You pawned the hairpin Mom gave you?

00:08:51.950 --> 00:08:53.430 line:80%
She would be upset.

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:59.280 line:80%
Don't worry.
I've struck a deal with Mr. Luo.

00:08:59.950 --> 00:09:02.760 line:80%
I'll redeem the hairpin
as soon as I earn enough money.

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:04.020 line:80%
Miss Fan, are you home?

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:06.550 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:09:07.470 --> 00:09:09.430 line:80%
Chef Li told me
to collect half a pig here.

00:09:09.430 --> 00:09:09.880 line:80%
Got it!

00:09:26.550 --> 00:09:28.070 line:80%
Here's the pay for the pork.

00:09:28.070 --> 00:09:28.760 line:80%
Thanks.

00:09:29.190 --> 00:09:30.070 line:80%
Take care!

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:42.160 line:80%
Changyu, when did you butcher that pig?

00:09:42.470 --> 00:09:43.880 line:80%
At the crack of dawn.

00:09:46.190 --> 00:09:47.280 line:80%
Stop telling everyone

00:09:47.280 --> 00:09:48.760 line:80%
that I'm a pig butcher.

00:09:49.830 --> 00:09:51.400 line:80%
Changyu, did you pawn the hairpin

00:09:51.400 --> 00:09:53.400 line:80%
to support that handsome young gentleman?

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:53.950 line:80%
Shh.

00:09:55.950 --> 00:09:57.190 line:80%
Keep it down.

00:09:57.190 --> 00:09:58.830 line:80%
Or people might hear us.

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:01.670 line:80%
I did it to save his life.

00:10:02.470 --> 00:10:03.880 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao was right.

00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:06.080 line:80%
The cost to support a man is high.

00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:08.600 line:80%
I have to work harder to make more money.

00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:12.630 line:80%
[South Market]

00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:17.230 line:80%
[Meat]

00:10:21.110 --> 00:10:27.450 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:01.820 line:80%
You're all sweaty.

00:11:04.950 --> 00:11:05.950 line:80%
Impressive, huh?

00:11:12.710 --> 00:11:14.430 line:80%
Dad, Mom, I brought food.

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:18.520 line:80%
Look,

00:11:19.160 --> 00:11:21.420 line:80%
you're all sweaty just like your father.

00:11:22.350 --> 00:11:23.160 line:80%
Let's eat.

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:24.010 line:80%
-Sure.
-Yes.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:24.580 line:80%
Come on.

00:11:26.950 --> 00:11:28.150 line:80%
These are yours, Dad.

00:11:28.470 --> 00:11:29.120 line:80%
Mom.

00:11:29.950 --> 00:11:30.710 line:80%
Here you are.

00:11:31.520 --> 00:11:32.400 line:80%
How is it, Dad?

00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:33.000 line:80%
Very good.

00:11:33.520 --> 00:11:35.190 line:80%
I really love your cooking.

00:11:37.710 --> 00:11:38.640 line:80%
Changyu.

00:11:39.590 --> 00:11:42.670 line:80%
Are you reopening
your family's butcher shop?

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:47.190 line:80%
Yes.

00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:50.750 line:80%
I'll continue what my parents started.

00:11:50.970 --> 00:11:53.470 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:11:51.550 --> 00:11:52.550 line:80%
Hello, welcome.

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:55.350 line:80%
How about this piece?

00:11:55.350 --> 00:11:56.590 line:80%
It's fresh.

00:11:58.250 --> 00:12:01.060 line:80%
[Boiled Dough Foods]

00:11:58.950 --> 00:12:00.920 line:80%
I guarantee it's fresh.

00:12:01.150 --> 00:12:02.950 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:03.760 line:80%
How much is the offal?

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:07.480 line:80%
[Meat]

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:05.070 line:80%
Ma'am,

00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:07.800 line:80%
offal is not sold separately today.

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:09.710 line:80%
This is the opening day of my shop.

00:12:09.710 --> 00:12:10.880 line:80%
For each catty of pork you buy,

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:12.160 line:80%
I'll throw in one tael of offal.

00:12:12.160 --> 00:12:13.470 line:80%
First come, first served.

00:12:13.470 --> 00:12:15.070 line:80%
Really? What a bargain.

00:12:16.070 --> 00:12:17.880 line:80%
I'll take... 5 catties of pork belly then.

00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:18.810 line:80%
Coming right up.

00:12:19.190 --> 00:12:21.160 line:80%
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty.

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:23.430 line:80%
But since you're the first customer today,

00:12:23.430 --> 00:12:25.230 line:80%
I'll lower the price to 18 maces.

00:12:25.800 --> 00:12:27.760 line:80%
You do know how to do business, miss.

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:29.430 line:80%
I'll buy from you again!

00:12:30.470 --> 00:12:31.200 line:80%
Here you are.

00:12:31.430 --> 00:12:32.270 line:80%
Take your pork.

00:12:32.270 --> 00:12:34.120 line:80%
Great.

00:12:35.550 --> 00:12:37.080 line:80%
And here is your free offal.

00:12:37.430 --> 00:12:38.470 line:80%
Thank you so much.

00:12:39.520 --> 00:12:40.550 line:80%
Here's the pay.

00:12:42.070 --> 00:12:42.760 line:80%
Take it. Thanks.

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:43.560 line:80%
Do come again!

00:12:43.830 --> 00:12:45.430 line:80%
I will, definitely.

00:12:45.430 --> 00:12:45.960 line:80%
Alright.

00:12:46.070 --> 00:12:47.640 line:80%
How much is this?

00:12:47.640 --> 00:12:48.950 line:80%
The meat is very fresh.

00:12:49.310 --> 00:12:51.280 line:80%
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty today.

00:12:51.280 --> 00:12:52.410 line:80%
I'll take one catty.

00:12:52.520 --> 00:12:53.670 line:80%
For each catty of pork you buy today,

00:12:53.670 --> 00:12:55.870 line:80%
I'll throw in one tael of braised offal.

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.310 line:80%
You can have this for free.

00:12:57.310 --> 00:12:59.640 line:80%
Changyu! Changyu!

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:01.280 line:80%
Changyu, stop selling pork this way!

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:02.090 line:80%
Mr. Guo!

00:13:02.560 --> 00:13:05.370 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:04.240 line:80%
One must not break the rules

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:05.670 line:80%
when doing business, right?

00:13:05.670 --> 00:13:06.950 line:80%
I know this is your shop's opening day.

00:13:06.950 --> 00:13:08.550 line:80%
Why do you have to offer offal for free?

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:08.660 line:80%
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:12.990 line:80%
[Meat]

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:09.760 line:80%
Mr. Guo,

00:13:09.890 --> 00:13:12.400 line:80%
I'm only giving a special offer
on this occasion

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.350 line:80%
for good luck.

00:13:13.830 --> 00:13:15.360 line:80%
How am I breaking the rules?

00:13:15.870 --> 00:13:17.870 line:80%
You are, with what you're doing now.

00:13:18.280 --> 00:13:20.920 line:80%
Is anyone else than you
giving away free offal?

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:22.640 line:80%
Enough, Guo Dali.

00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:24.350 line:80%
Why bicker with a young girl?

00:13:24.350 --> 00:13:26.010 line:80%
She's only selling half a pig.

00:13:26.070 --> 00:13:28.150 line:80%
I'm talking to her.
How is it involving you now?

00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:29.770 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:13:28.150 --> 00:13:29.340 line:80%
Yeah, Mr. Guo.

00:13:29.920 --> 00:13:31.800 line:80%
Are you picking on me

00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:34.760 line:80%
because I'm parentless
and all by my lonesome?

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:36.160 line:80%
Exactly!

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:37.590 line:80%
How can you do this?

00:13:37.760 --> 00:13:39.640 line:80%
It's wrong to bully this young girl.

00:13:39.640 --> 00:13:40.900 line:80%
You're way out of line!

00:13:41.880 --> 00:13:43.190 line:80%
Fine, fine, fine.

00:13:43.830 --> 00:13:45.070 line:80%
Today is an exception then.

00:13:45.070 --> 00:13:47.130 line:80%
Don't throw in offal again tomorrow.

00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:48.070 line:80%
Got it!

00:13:48.310 --> 00:13:50.770 line:80%
This policy was meant to last one day
anyway.

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:52.190 line:80%
Go with it then.

00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:54.640 line:80%
You're a real meddler!

00:13:55.550 --> 00:13:57.410 line:80%
I need to save some for sale later.

00:14:00.070 --> 00:14:02.760 line:80%
Fan's Butcher Shop has just opened!

00:14:02.920 --> 00:14:04.640 line:80%
Buy pork and get free braised offal!

00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:05.760 line:80%
Twenty maces per catty!

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.070 line:80%
Day-fresh pork!

00:14:07.670 --> 00:14:09.640 line:80%
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty today.

00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:10.520 line:80%
How much would you like?

00:14:10.110 --> 00:14:12.440 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:14:10.520 --> 00:14:11.070 line:80%
I'll take one catty.

00:14:11.070 --> 00:14:11.690 line:80%
One catty, right?

00:14:11.690 --> 00:14:12.890 line:80%
Three catties for me!

00:14:13.190 --> 00:14:14.590 line:80%
Two hundred and seventy.

00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:16.680 line:80%
Two hundred and eighty.

00:14:17.470 --> 00:14:18.800 line:80%
Two hundred and ninety.

00:14:18.920 --> 00:14:19.710 line:80%
Changyu!

00:14:20.310 --> 00:14:21.190 line:80%
Changyu!

00:14:20.580 --> 00:14:23.140 line:80%
[Butcher Shop]

00:14:22.760 --> 00:14:26.160 line:80%
-Mr. Zhao, listen, today, I've earned...
-You listen to me first.

00:14:26.160 --> 00:14:29.520 line:80%
Your uncle brought some goons
from the gambling house to your place.

00:14:29.520 --> 00:14:32.000 line:80%
They're turning your home upside down
for the title deed.

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:32.760 line:80%
What?

00:14:35.430 --> 00:14:37.330 line:80%
[Butcher Shop]

00:14:35.520 --> 00:14:36.400 line:80%
Filthy scum.

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:37.590 line:80%
Changyu!

00:14:37.950 --> 00:14:40.760 line:80%
Why are you carrying that knife?
Don't make unwise decisions!

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:47.540 line:80%
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:43.000 line:80%
Oh no. She's going to kill.

00:14:48.350 --> 00:14:50.160 line:80%
Song Yan, open the door!

00:14:50.670 --> 00:14:51.520 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:14:53.830 --> 00:14:54.800 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:14:55.950 --> 00:14:56.760 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:59.430 line:80%
Song Yan,
Fan Erniu and his wife treated you well.

00:14:59.430 --> 00:15:01.760 line:80%
You should come out and defend Changyu!

00:15:03.640 --> 00:15:04.550 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:09.120 line:80%
Song Yan, open the door!

00:15:09.310 --> 00:15:11.000 line:80%
I know you're in there!

00:15:11.240 --> 00:15:12.190 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:13.190 --> 00:15:14.160 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:14.640 --> 00:15:15.590 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:17.520 line:80%
A life is at stake!

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:18.710 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:20.280 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:21.120 --> 00:15:21.880 line:80%
Sit down.

00:15:22.550 --> 00:15:23.830 line:80%
Focus on your studies.

00:15:24.640 --> 00:15:25.400 line:80%
Mother,

00:15:26.280 --> 00:15:27.310 line:80%
Changyu is in trouble.

00:15:27.310 --> 00:15:28.310 line:80%
I must go help her.

00:15:28.640 --> 00:15:31.800 line:80%
Fan Daniu is Fan Changyu's uncle.

00:15:32.190 --> 00:15:33.310 line:80%
This is essentially

00:15:33.310 --> 00:15:35.190 line:80%
an affair within the Fan family.

00:15:35.590 --> 00:15:37.670 line:80%
What does it have to do
with us the Song family?

00:15:37.670 --> 00:15:39.880 line:80%
How can I contribute to the country
if I can't even help a family?

00:15:39.880 --> 00:15:41.470 line:80%
Why should I take the imperial exam
and strive

00:15:41.470 --> 00:15:42.550 line:80%
to become an official if I just ignore

00:15:42.550 --> 00:15:44.000 line:80%
an ongoing dispute near my doorsteps?

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:45.400 line:80%
Stepping out of this door

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:49.330 line:80%
is bidding farewell
to scholarly honors and official careers.

00:15:49.550 --> 00:15:50.430 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:15:50.880 --> 00:15:53.280 line:80%
Have you learned nothing from those books?

00:15:53.800 --> 00:15:55.190 line:80%
Do you have no respect

00:15:55.190 --> 00:15:57.550 line:80%
for your father's dignity and pride
at all?

00:15:57.550 --> 00:15:58.400 line:80%
Son,

00:15:59.710 --> 00:16:01.310 line:80%
we went to such great lengths

00:16:01.590 --> 00:16:03.760 line:80%
to cancel your engagement to that jinx.

00:16:03.760 --> 00:16:05.950 line:80%
If you stand up for her today,

00:16:06.350 --> 00:16:08.710 line:80%
you'll give a chance
to those gossipmongers

00:16:08.710 --> 00:16:10.910 line:80%
to tarnish your reputation, won't you?

00:16:12.280 --> 00:16:14.760 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, stop yelling.

00:16:15.470 --> 00:16:17.730 line:80%
Song Yan is no longer engaged to Changyu.

00:16:17.800 --> 00:16:20.310 line:80%
Why would he and his mother help her?

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:21.920 line:80%
Enough, Granny Kang.

00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:23.920 line:80%
Changyu is pitiful
just because her parents died?

00:16:23.920 --> 00:16:26.000 line:80%
My mother passed away a long time ago too.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:27.430 line:80%
Has anyone pitied me?

00:16:27.430 --> 00:16:28.760 line:80%
Stop it.

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:30.160 line:80%
Song Yan!

00:16:30.430 --> 00:16:32.120 line:80%
Song Yan, open the door now!

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:34.280 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

00:16:34.920 --> 00:16:36.400 line:80%
What's going on with Changning?

00:16:36.400 --> 00:16:38.240 line:80%
She's been gasping for breath.

00:16:41.520 --> 00:16:42.350 line:80%
Changning!

00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:44.430 line:80%
Changning!

00:16:44.430 --> 00:16:45.950 line:80%
Don't be afraid.

00:16:48.400 --> 00:16:49.730 line:80%
Sniff it. Nice and slow.

00:16:50.280 --> 00:16:51.190 line:80%
No rush.

00:16:53.470 --> 00:16:54.400 line:80%
Changyu's here.

00:16:55.190 --> 00:16:56.790 line:80%
She's even carrying a knife.

00:16:56.830 --> 00:16:58.560 line:80%
She's not going to kill, is she?

00:16:58.880 --> 00:17:00.760 line:80%
Shortly after her father's death,

00:17:00.760 --> 00:17:02.590 line:80%
her uncle's already trying to seize
her and her sister's property.

00:17:02.590 --> 00:17:04.389 line:80%
Even a rabbit will bite when cornered.

00:17:04.389 --> 00:17:05.200 line:80%
Changning,

00:17:05.240 --> 00:17:06.840 line:80%
-Are you alright?
-Changyu.

00:17:08.520 --> 00:17:09.720 line:80%
Mrs. Zhuang, Mrs. Zhao,

00:17:09.720 --> 00:17:10.680 line:80%
take care of Changning for me.

00:17:10.680 --> 00:17:11.389 line:80%
Sure.

00:17:20.550 --> 00:17:21.629 line:80%
Let's go.

00:17:26.110 --> 00:17:27.629 line:80%
Let's see if we can help.

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:42.290 line:80%
Stop what you're doing!

00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:46.280 line:80%
Changyu, you're finally back.

00:17:51.930 --> 00:17:55.760 line:80%
[Jin Yuanbao]

00:17:54.280 --> 00:17:55.590 line:80%
You're back, Miss Fan.

00:17:58.070 --> 00:17:59.000 line:80%
Take your men...

00:18:00.070 --> 00:18:01.200 line:80%
and get out of here.

00:18:03.110 --> 00:18:05.970 line:80%
Things work by certain rules
in the gambling house.

00:18:06.110 --> 00:18:08.240 line:80%
Fan Daniu claimed this house to be his,

00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:10.690 line:80%
so I came to look for the title deed,

00:18:13.150 --> 00:18:15.410 line:80%
with which he'll pay his gambling debts.

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:17.450 line:80%
You told them you owned this house?

00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:20.590 line:80%
Changyu...

00:18:22.350 --> 00:18:24.960 line:80%
I didn't have a better choice.

00:18:25.520 --> 00:18:26.680 line:80%
M-M-My dear niece,

00:18:26.870 --> 00:18:28.720 line:80%
please do your uncle a favor.

00:18:28.510 --> 00:18:30.870 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:18:29.070 --> 00:18:31.630 line:80%
Please give them the house
to pay off my debts.

00:18:31.650 --> 00:18:32.510 line:80%
I promise I will

00:18:33.110 --> 00:18:35.440 line:80%
treat you and Changning

00:18:35.440 --> 00:18:37.680 line:80%
like my own daughters from now on.

00:18:37.680 --> 00:18:38.720 line:80%
Alright?

00:18:39.800 --> 00:18:42.150 line:80%
Why not give them your house instead?

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:44.760 line:80%
But where are my wife and I

00:18:44.760 --> 00:18:46.480 line:80%
supposed to live that way?

00:18:46.870 --> 00:18:49.630 line:80%
Changning and you will both get married
in the future.

00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:51.760 line:80%
This house will be of no use to you then.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:56.480 line:80%
What Changning and I do with
the stuff left by our parents

00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:57.880 line:80%
is none of your business.

00:18:58.240 --> 00:18:59.240 line:80%
Did you hear that?

00:18:59.390 --> 00:19:00.850 line:80%
He doesn't own this house.

00:19:01.550 --> 00:19:03.870 line:80%
I'm your uncle. I...

00:19:04.630 --> 00:19:05.230 line:80%
Come here!

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:06.560 line:80%
Come here!

00:19:06.760 --> 00:19:08.350 line:80%
-Mr. Jin, Mr. Jin...
-Don't move!

00:19:08.350 --> 00:19:08.960 line:80%
Mr. Jin!

00:19:10.280 --> 00:19:12.540 line:80%
If you don't give me the title deed today,

00:19:13.390 --> 00:19:14.830 line:80%
I'll have to chop off a hand of his

00:19:14.830 --> 00:19:16.160 line:80%
and show it to the brass.

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:18.870 line:80%
I'll count to three.

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:21.200 line:80%
One.

00:19:22.760 --> 00:19:23.440 line:80%
Two.

00:19:28.480 --> 00:19:29.680 line:80%
Use this cleaver.

00:19:30.310 --> 00:19:31.150 line:80%
It's sharp.

00:19:31.590 --> 00:19:33.120 line:80%
One chop's enough to cut off

00:19:33.480 --> 00:19:35.480 line:80%
the skin, flesh, muscles and bones.

00:19:35.870 --> 00:19:38.200 line:80%
It'll spare my uncle from some suffering.

00:19:40.350 --> 00:19:42.480 line:80%
You... You...

00:19:43.630 --> 00:19:44.960 line:80%
You're joking, right?

00:19:44.960 --> 00:19:46.630 line:80%
You started this joke first.

00:19:54.350 --> 00:19:55.480 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:57.910 line:80%
Your parents both died
because you're a jinx!

00:19:57.910 --> 00:20:00.560 line:80%
Are you also going to have me,
your own uncle, killed now?

00:20:00.560 --> 00:20:03.390 line:80%
Nobody wants you, little miss.
Even your fiancé ditched you.

00:20:03.390 --> 00:20:06.110 line:80%
How dare you keep this house
as your dowry?

00:20:03.420 --> 00:20:05.080 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:20:06.110 --> 00:20:07.590 line:80%
Will any man put his life at risk

00:20:07.590 --> 00:20:09.150 line:80%
and marry you, a jinx?

00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:12.800 line:80%
You...

00:20:14.680 --> 00:20:16.280 line:80%
get out of my sight right now.

00:20:16.390 --> 00:20:18.440 line:80%
Otherwise, unlike them,
I won't take your hand,

00:20:18.440 --> 00:20:19.590 line:80%
but your life!

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:21.130 line:80%
I'll kill you first,

00:20:21.830 --> 00:20:23.830 line:80%
and then myself
as an apology to my parents!

00:20:23.830 --> 00:20:24.630 line:80%
Miss Fan,

00:20:25.720 --> 00:20:28.110 line:80%
we from the gambling house are
reasonable people.

00:20:28.110 --> 00:20:29.570 line:80%
The Legal Code of Great Yin

00:20:29.870 --> 00:20:32.520 line:80%
says that the property of a citizen
who has no male heir

00:20:32.520 --> 00:20:35.440 line:80%
should be inherited by the closest kin,
such as brothers.

00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:37.390 line:80%
Even if you take this matter
to the magistrate's office,

00:20:37.390 --> 00:20:40.050 line:80%
this house will be awarded
to Fan Daniu the same.

00:20:41.150 --> 00:20:42.110 line:80%
That's right.

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:45.650 line:80%
Those from the gambling house
are truly reasonable.

00:20:46.310 --> 00:20:48.680 line:80%
Now that the Legal Code of Great Yin
also supports that I have this house,

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:50.280 line:80%
what are you lot waiting for?

00:20:50.520 --> 00:20:51.590 line:80%
Continue to...

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:55.370 line:80%
look for the title deed for Mr. Jin!

00:20:56.510 --> 00:20:59.530 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:21:00.960 --> 00:21:02.110 line:80%
Search carefully.

00:21:31.910 --> 00:21:36.310 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:21:43.350 --> 00:21:44.000 line:80%
Dad,

00:21:45.110 --> 00:21:46.910 line:80%
if I defiantly break your rules,

00:21:49.240 --> 00:21:50.370 line:80%
please don't be mad.

00:21:52.590 --> 00:21:53.440 line:80%
Changning!

00:21:54.550 --> 00:21:56.150 line:80%
Turn around and count to ten.

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:04.240 line:80%
One.

00:22:08.800 --> 00:22:10.020 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:22:10.940 --> 00:22:12.180 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:22:11.870 --> 00:22:12.760 line:80%
Two.

00:22:18.630 --> 00:22:19.680 line:80%
Three.

00:22:23.760 --> 00:22:24.760 line:80%
Four.

00:22:31.720 --> 00:22:32.910 line:80%
Five.

00:22:44.390 --> 00:22:45.630 line:80%
Six.

00:22:53.680 --> 00:22:54.760 line:80%
Seven.

00:22:58.800 --> 00:23:00.830 line:80%
Will you go away or not?

00:23:00.830 --> 00:23:01.760 line:80%
Eight.

00:23:02.480 --> 00:23:04.410 line:80%
You idiots. Team up and attack her!

00:23:07.070 --> 00:23:08.070 line:80%
Nine.

00:23:26.110 --> 00:23:28.240 line:80%
I've only counted to nine.

00:23:29.720 --> 00:23:32.150 line:80%
I might as well quit this business

00:23:33.390 --> 00:23:35.190 line:80%
if I let a young girl beat me down!

00:23:37.350 --> 00:23:38.440 line:80%
Watch out!

00:23:55.760 --> 00:23:59.110 line:80%
You're ganging up on a parentless girl
in broad daylight!

00:23:59.350 --> 00:24:01.000 line:80%
Where is your...

00:24:22.200 --> 00:24:22.800 line:80%
My Lord.

00:24:26.480 --> 00:24:28.740 line:80%
All the damaged items are recorded here.

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:30.000 line:80%
Pay for these,

00:24:30.310 --> 00:24:32.110 line:80%
and this matter will be settled.

00:24:36.950 --> 00:24:37.790 line:80%
Jin Yuanbao,

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:40.520 line:80%
you're 27 years old now, aren't you?

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:43.440 line:80%
Instead of raising a family
and pursuing a career,

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:45.200 line:80%
you're stirring up trouble all the time.

00:24:45.200 --> 00:24:46.930 line:80%
Can you face your grandmother?

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:50.110 line:80%
W-We'll pay for her losses.

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:52.310 line:80%
Then who will pay for our medical bills?

00:24:52.310 --> 00:24:54.630 line:80%
The four muscular men of you
were defeated by a woman.

00:24:54.630 --> 00:24:54.870 line:80%
I...

00:24:54.870 --> 00:24:56.550 line:80%
And you have the gall to ask her
to foot your medical bills?

00:24:56.550 --> 00:24:57.350 line:80%
Get lost now.

00:24:58.590 --> 00:24:59.440 line:80%
Wait!

00:25:02.330 --> 00:25:11.840 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:25:05.960 --> 00:25:08.620 line:80%
You knocked over
my parents' memorial tablets.

00:25:10.590 --> 00:25:12.650 line:80%
You can't leave until you apologize.

00:25:13.390 --> 00:25:14.150 line:80%
Officer,

00:25:14.760 --> 00:25:17.070 line:80%
I should be the owner of this house.

00:25:17.070 --> 00:25:18.630 line:80%
If you have problems about its ownership,

00:25:18.630 --> 00:25:21.000 line:80%
then write a complaint
and submit it to the magistrate's office.

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:21.550 line:80%
I...

00:25:22.390 --> 00:25:23.830 line:80%
For damaging these memorial tablets,

00:25:23.830 --> 00:25:25.150 line:80%
you'll be flogged 20 times

00:25:25.150 --> 00:25:26.550 line:80%
if she decides to sue you.

00:25:31.950 --> 00:25:32.760 line:80%
Mr. Fan Erniu,

00:25:32.760 --> 00:25:33.680 line:80%
Ms. Meng Lihua,

00:25:34.070 --> 00:25:34.800 line:80%
we're sorry.

00:25:34.910 --> 00:25:35.590 line:80%
We're sorry.

00:25:35.590 --> 00:25:36.650 line:80%
Please forgive us.

00:25:37.060 --> 00:25:37.900 line:80%
We apologize!

00:25:37.850 --> 00:25:40.340 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:25:38.240 --> 00:25:39.110 line:80%
We apologize!

00:25:39.390 --> 00:25:40.240 line:80%
We apologize.

00:25:47.310 --> 00:25:48.840 line:80%
I'll leave this money here.

00:25:53.830 --> 00:25:54.630 line:80%
You may go now.

00:25:59.830 --> 00:26:01.760 line:80%
Come on. A word in private.

00:26:01.870 --> 00:26:03.550 line:80%
-Go!
-Mr. Jin, Mr. Jin...

00:26:03.590 --> 00:26:04.090 line:80%
Mr. Jin.

00:26:04.150 --> 00:26:04.630 line:80%
Mr. Jin!

00:26:10.440 --> 00:26:11.480 line:80%
Keep this safe for your sister.

00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:12.480 line:80%
I knew it was right

00:26:12.830 --> 00:26:14.310 line:80%
to ask you to come over.

00:26:15.350 --> 00:26:17.210 line:80%
Though Fan Erniu is gone forever,

00:26:17.240 --> 00:26:19.200 line:80%
your friendship with him remains.

00:26:19.310 --> 00:26:21.200 line:80%
But I'm afraid Fan Daniu won't stop

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:22.600 line:80%
fighting for this house.

00:26:25.110 --> 00:26:25.960 line:80%
Changyu.

00:26:29.910 --> 00:26:30.760 line:80%
Changyu!

00:26:32.830 --> 00:26:35.960 line:80%
A young girl has to sustain
an entire household alone...

00:26:36.830 --> 00:26:38.310 line:80%
How unfortunate.

00:26:39.420 --> 00:26:44.500 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]

00:26:41.830 --> 00:26:42.520 line:80%
Dad,

00:26:43.720 --> 00:26:45.920 line:80%
you told me to never let anyone see me use

00:26:46.210 --> 00:26:53.020 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:26:46.440 --> 00:26:48.310 line:80%
the long-handled blade techniques
you taught me

00:26:48.310 --> 00:26:50.440 line:80%
except in the face of imminent danger.

00:26:51.590 --> 00:26:53.450 line:80%
But I disobeyed your order today.

00:26:54.070 --> 00:26:56.150 line:80%
I beg for your forgiveness, Dad, Mom.

00:26:59.390 --> 00:27:01.520 line:80%
I'm sure your father will forgive you.

00:27:05.070 --> 00:27:06.530 line:80%
You're severely injured.

00:27:06.550 --> 00:27:07.720 line:80%
Why did you come out

00:27:07.910 --> 00:27:09.440 line:80%
instead of resting inside?

00:27:09.800 --> 00:27:11.200 line:80%
There was too much noise.

00:27:11.390 --> 00:27:13.190 line:80%
I thought I'd come out for a look.

00:27:19.060 --> 00:27:21.600 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:27:22.350 --> 00:27:23.550 line:80%
"Fan Erniu..."

00:27:26.440 --> 00:27:28.500 line:80%
So your father was not only a butcher,

00:27:29.680 --> 00:27:31.540 line:80%
but also a martial practitioner.

00:27:32.800 --> 00:27:33.910 line:80%
You heard all that?

00:27:37.910 --> 00:27:39.840 line:80%
Before my father became a butcher,

00:27:40.150 --> 00:27:41.750 line:80%
he worked as an armed escort.

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:44.820 line:80%
Your mother was named Meng Lihua.

00:27:46.480 --> 00:27:47.740 line:80%
Was that her real name?

00:27:50.110 --> 00:27:51.640 line:80%
Yes. My mother was amazing.

00:27:52.910 --> 00:27:54.110 line:80%
She was literate.

00:27:56.110 --> 00:27:57.570 line:80%
She composed fragrances.

00:27:58.680 --> 00:27:59.740 line:80%
The other butchers

00:28:00.150 --> 00:28:01.310 line:80%
and their homes reek

00:28:02.280 --> 00:28:03.810 line:80%
when pigs are slaughtered.

00:28:04.200 --> 00:28:05.730 line:80%
But my home is an exception.

00:28:06.280 --> 00:28:08.110 line:80%
All our washed clothes would be scented

00:28:08.110 --> 00:28:10.110 line:80%
with the incense made by my mother

00:28:12.110 --> 00:28:13.570 line:80%
to purge all the bad odors.

00:28:14.070 --> 00:28:14.680 line:80%
Folks,

00:28:14.870 --> 00:28:15.680 line:80%
there's nothing to see here.

00:28:15.680 --> 00:28:16.800 line:80%
Stop watching, folks.

00:28:16.800 --> 00:28:17.550 line:80%
Dismissed!

00:28:17.550 --> 00:28:18.960 line:80%
-Leave!
-Go home!

00:28:20.200 --> 00:28:21.070 line:80%
Thank you.

00:28:21.520 --> 00:28:23.650 line:80%
Today, those people were in the wrong.

00:28:25.630 --> 00:28:27.110 line:80%
But they did make a point.

00:28:27.520 --> 00:28:29.650 line:80%
If Fan Daniu really files a complaint,

00:28:30.070 --> 00:28:32.150 line:80%
Changyu will probably lose her house.

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:33.680 line:80%
Is there anything we can do?

00:28:33.760 --> 00:28:36.150 line:80%
Changyu and her sister
are all by themselves.

00:28:36.150 --> 00:28:37.800 line:80%
You must help them.

00:28:38.070 --> 00:28:39.670 line:80%
I didn't say I wouldn't help.

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:47.100 line:80%
There is actually a solution.

00:28:49.110 --> 00:28:54.200 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:28:49.800 --> 00:28:52.150 line:80%
How did your parents pass away?

00:28:53.240 --> 00:28:54.310 line:80%
They met bandits.

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:56.600 line:80%
My father's throat was slit.

00:28:57.310 --> 00:28:58.390 line:80%
He died on the spot.

00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:02.770 line:80%
My mother was drawing her last breath
when she was brought home.

00:29:04.910 --> 00:29:07.370 line:80%
She hung in there
for six to eight whole hours

00:29:09.070 --> 00:29:11.110 line:80%
just to speak to me and my sister.

00:29:14.870 --> 00:29:17.200 line:80%
But she didn't manage to say
a single word.

00:29:22.870 --> 00:29:25.930 line:80%
All she could do was give me the hairpin
she was holding.

00:29:28.960 --> 00:29:31.290 line:80%
Your parents definitely won't blame you.

00:29:34.870 --> 00:29:36.930 line:80%
This gauze isn't stained with blood.

00:29:37.070 --> 00:29:37.760 line:80%
It's clean.

00:29:41.280 --> 00:29:42.070 line:80%
Thanks.

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:44.020 line:80%
Unlike me, at least

00:29:44.590 --> 00:29:46.990 line:80%
your parents were with you
when you grew up.

00:29:49.390 --> 00:29:51.280 line:80%
At least you still have your sister,

00:29:51.280 --> 00:29:52.720 line:80%
your own flesh and blood.

00:29:54.110 --> 00:29:55.000 line:80%
At least...

00:29:55.280 --> 00:29:57.960 line:80%
you still have your home
where you've lived for many years.

00:29:57.960 --> 00:29:59.350 line:80%
By contrast, my parents

00:30:00.870 --> 00:30:02.400 line:80%
were gone when I was little.

00:30:05.350 --> 00:30:07.150 line:80%
How did they pass away?

00:30:16.550 --> 00:30:17.750 line:80%
War took their lives.

00:30:26.000 --> 00:30:29.070 line:80%
Well, as parentless children,

00:30:30.390 --> 00:30:32.650 line:80%
we shouldn't be comparing our miseries.

00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:34.830 line:80%
Sorry.

00:30:35.440 --> 00:30:37.440 line:80%
I reminded you of your painful past.

00:30:40.350 --> 00:30:42.210 line:80%
You've figured out the truth now.

00:30:43.310 --> 00:30:45.590 line:80%
I'm just a butcher with brute strength.

00:30:46.310 --> 00:30:47.550 line:80%
Laugh if you want.

00:30:51.480 --> 00:30:52.940 line:80%
You not only saved my life,

00:30:53.960 --> 00:30:55.590 line:80%
but also have been trying to raise money

00:30:55.590 --> 00:30:56.590 line:80%
to provide for me.

00:30:57.440 --> 00:30:58.590 line:80%
Wouldn't it make me an ingrate

00:30:58.590 --> 00:31:00.000 line:80%
to laugh at you?

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:08.310 line:80%
Changyu! Changyu!

00:31:08.480 --> 00:31:10.390 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao wants to see you.

00:31:10.910 --> 00:31:12.370 line:80%
Don't tell anyone I cried.

00:31:14.350 --> 00:31:14.880 line:80%
Let's go.

00:31:16.310 --> 00:31:16.960 line:80%
Careful.

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:21.280 line:80%
Will he get well?

00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:22.310 line:80%
Will he fully recover?

00:31:22.310 --> 00:31:25.760 line:80%
At worst, there might be
lingering issues in his legs.

00:31:25.960 --> 00:31:26.760 line:80%
His other body parts will be fine.

00:31:26.760 --> 00:31:27.890 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao!

00:31:28.520 --> 00:31:29.850 line:80%
There you are, Changyu.

00:31:30.280 --> 00:31:31.240 line:80%
Come on in.

00:31:32.440 --> 00:31:34.700 line:80%
We'd like to discuss something with you.

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:38.440 line:80%
Look at the snow on your head.

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:39.630 line:80%
What's the matter?

00:31:40.110 --> 00:31:41.170 line:80%
Why so mysterious?

00:31:58.910 --> 00:32:00.680 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, just speak your mind.

00:32:00.680 --> 00:32:02.080 line:80%
I'll do whatever you say.

00:32:08.350 --> 00:32:09.880 line:80%
Have a matrilocal husband?

00:32:12.310 --> 00:32:14.630 line:80%
It's Constable Wang's idea.

00:32:14.630 --> 00:32:15.550 line:80%
Best advice ever.

00:32:15.550 --> 00:32:16.800 line:80%
Look, this way,

00:32:16.870 --> 00:32:18.910 line:80%
there will be a male heir to your father,

00:32:18.910 --> 00:32:20.440 line:80%
and you can keep your house.

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:22.520 line:80%
Fan Daniu won't be able to snatch it away.

00:32:22.520 --> 00:32:23.800 line:80%
This house is all

00:32:23.910 --> 00:32:26.000 line:80%
your parents left for you and your sister.

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.440 line:80%
If it's gone,

00:32:27.800 --> 00:32:29.350 line:80%
how are you supposed to live?

00:32:29.350 --> 00:32:31.720 line:80%
Yeah. Parents usually choose husbands

00:32:31.870 --> 00:32:34.150 line:80%
carefully for their daughters.

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:36.520 line:80%
Changyu really lives a bitter life.

00:32:36.520 --> 00:32:39.070 line:80%
What decent young man would agree
to be a matrilocal husband?

00:32:39.070 --> 00:32:40.870 line:80%
Extreme conditions call for
extreme solutions, right?

00:32:40.870 --> 00:32:42.280 line:80%
Changyu has to find a matrilocal husband

00:32:42.280 --> 00:32:43.960 line:80%
if she is to keep her house.

00:32:44.350 --> 00:32:46.000 line:80%
What's a matrilocal husband?

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:47.720 line:80%
That refers to...

00:32:47.720 --> 00:32:49.200 line:80%
a man who your sister

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:50.800 line:80%
will spend the rest of her life with,

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:52.730 line:80%
and who can take care of you and her.

00:32:53.480 --> 00:32:55.440 line:80%
Then I want that handsome young gentleman
to be this man.

00:32:55.440 --> 00:32:56.390 line:80%
Not him!

00:32:57.070 --> 00:32:58.070 line:80%
Why not?

00:32:58.590 --> 00:33:01.480 line:80%
Based on my ten-odd years
of matchmaking experience,

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:03.210 line:80%
I can tell he's a decent fellow.

00:33:04.070 --> 00:33:05.600 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, as you just said,

00:33:05.910 --> 00:33:08.240 line:80%
what decent young fellow would agree
to be a matrilocal husband?

00:33:08.240 --> 00:33:10.630 line:80%
My wife has been a matchmaker
for over a decade.

00:33:10.630 --> 00:33:13.000 line:80%
She's seen more young men
than you've seen pigs.

00:33:13.000 --> 00:33:15.330 line:80%
You should take her expert advice on this.

00:33:15.830 --> 00:33:18.520 line:80%
Besides,
Chongzhou is an active combat zone now.

00:33:18.520 --> 00:33:20.280 line:80%
I heard the military would launch
a recruitment again.

00:33:20.280 --> 00:33:22.830 line:80%
Every family's hurrying
to arrange marriages now,

00:33:22.830 --> 00:33:24.560 line:80%
just to ensure they have heirs.

00:33:24.680 --> 00:33:25.870 line:80%
Finding a matrilocal husband

00:33:25.870 --> 00:33:27.910 line:80%
is even harder than reaching the heavens!

00:33:27.910 --> 00:33:28.720 line:80%
Yan Zheng can't be my husband.

00:33:28.720 --> 00:33:29.630 line:80%
Why can't he?

00:33:29.630 --> 00:33:30.590 line:80%
He just can't!

00:33:30.590 --> 00:33:31.350 line:80%
But why?

00:33:31.680 --> 00:33:32.230 line:80%
He...

00:33:32.230 --> 00:33:33.550 line:80%
Alright. Keep it down.

00:33:35.150 --> 00:33:36.390 line:80%
Yan Zheng

00:33:36.830 --> 00:33:38.630 line:80%
is badly injured

00:33:39.520 --> 00:33:42.590 line:80%
and will probably have trouble
with his legs after he recovers.

00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:44.800 line:80%
He even doesn't have identity papers
or travel permits.

00:33:44.800 --> 00:33:45.680 line:80%
Nonetheless,

00:33:46.630 --> 00:33:47.720 line:80%
the silver lining

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:50.150 line:80%
is that he's a choice within your reach!

00:33:50.150 --> 00:33:50.760 line:80%
Right?

00:33:50.830 --> 00:33:53.390 line:80%
Changyu, this is a win-win opportunity

00:33:53.390 --> 00:33:54.520 line:80%
for both of you.

00:33:54.760 --> 00:33:56.350 line:80%
Neither of you are taking advantage
of each other.

00:33:56.350 --> 00:33:57.810 line:80%
-But...
-My wife's right.

00:33:57.910 --> 00:33:59.720 line:80%
You just promised to do

00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:00.550 line:80%
whatever I say.

00:34:00.550 --> 00:34:01.480 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao...

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:02.280 line:80%
Knock it off!

00:34:02.720 --> 00:34:03.590 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:34:04.720 --> 00:34:07.850 line:80%
I know you both want what's the best
for Changning and me.

00:34:07.990 --> 00:34:10.350 line:80%
But please let me mull it over.

00:34:11.510 --> 00:34:13.120 line:80%
What is there to think about?

00:34:13.720 --> 00:34:14.910 line:80%
-Changyu.
-Changyu!

00:34:14.910 --> 00:34:16.110 line:80%
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

00:34:22.950 --> 00:34:24.200 line:80%
Why are you sighing?

00:34:34.120 --> 00:34:35.080 line:80%
Changyu,

00:34:35.830 --> 00:34:37.080 line:80%
tell me what you think

00:34:37.600 --> 00:34:39.200 line:80%
is wrong with that lad.

00:34:43.950 --> 00:34:44.749 line:80%
Do you mean...

00:34:45.080 --> 00:34:46.410 line:80%
he can't perform in bed?

00:34:48.240 --> 00:34:48.830 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:34:48.830 --> 00:34:49.830 line:80%
I'll ask my husband

00:34:49.830 --> 00:34:51.160 line:80%
if there's a cure.

00:34:51.310 --> 00:34:52.910 line:80%
That's not what I mean.

00:34:53.350 --> 00:34:54.880 line:80%
Don't read too much into it.

00:34:56.080 --> 00:34:58.340 line:80%
What if Yan Zheng rejects this proposal?

00:34:59.310 --> 00:35:01.640 line:80%
You're a beautiful young lady
who can provide for the family

00:35:01.640 --> 00:35:02.950 line:80%
by butchering pigs.

00:35:03.310 --> 00:35:04.710 line:80%
Who is he to turn you down?

00:35:05.200 --> 00:35:07.760 line:80%
Besides, he doesn't have identity papers
or travel permits.

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:08.600 line:80%
If he marries you,

00:35:08.600 --> 00:35:09.950 line:80%
at least he won't be taken for a refugee

00:35:09.950 --> 00:35:11.800 line:80%
and sent to the Vanguard Battalion.

00:35:11.800 --> 00:35:13.950 line:80%
How can I force him
to be a matrilocal husband

00:35:13.950 --> 00:35:15.210 line:80%
after I just saved him?

00:35:16.280 --> 00:35:18.340 line:80%
It's blackmail through owed favors.

00:35:20.160 --> 00:35:22.120 line:80%
His opinion aside,

00:35:22.910 --> 00:35:24.120 line:80%
he'll inevitably

00:35:26.600 --> 00:35:28.660 line:80%
become the same as Song Yan over time.

00:35:31.950 --> 00:35:34.680 line:80%
Scholars always betray
those who love them.

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:37.430 line:80%
But Yan Zheng is not a scholar.

00:35:37.830 --> 00:35:40.090 line:80%
He's nothing like that ingrate Song Yan.

00:35:44.600 --> 00:35:45.390 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao,

00:35:46.720 --> 00:35:48.080 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:35:49.310 --> 00:35:50.990 line:80%
is like a piece of tallow white jade

00:35:50.990 --> 00:35:53.200 line:80%
that I stumbled upon in the snow—

00:35:54.160 --> 00:35:54.910 line:80%
beautiful,

00:35:55.830 --> 00:35:56.470 line:80%
lustrous,

00:35:57.200 --> 00:35:58.080 line:80%
and valuable.

00:35:59.120 --> 00:36:00.850 line:80%
But I don't own this jade piece,

00:36:01.430 --> 00:36:03.310 line:80%
not even if it's carved

00:36:03.310 --> 00:36:04.430 line:80%
with my name on it.

00:36:04.950 --> 00:36:07.310 line:80%
Then put your name on it
and keep it for yourself for now.

00:36:07.310 --> 00:36:08.510 line:80%
If anyone comes looking for it,

00:36:08.510 --> 00:36:09.990 line:80%
we'll return it.

00:36:12.310 --> 00:36:13.720 line:80%
Yan Zheng already said

00:36:14.680 --> 00:36:16.510 line:80%
that he'd leave upon recovery.

00:36:17.800 --> 00:36:20.430 line:80%
When he has a wonderful girl like you
as his wife

00:36:20.430 --> 00:36:21.510 line:80%
and leads a stable life here,

00:36:21.510 --> 00:36:22.800 line:80%
will he ever want to leave?

00:36:22.800 --> 00:36:25.680 line:80%
He'll probably stick around
even if you tell him to go!

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:27.280 line:80%
My dearest Mrs. Zhao,

00:36:27.720 --> 00:36:30.870 line:80%
it's not a good idea to coerce him
into marrying a butcher.

00:36:30.870 --> 00:36:32.470 line:80%
Forced fruit is never sweet.

00:36:33.160 --> 00:36:35.640 line:80%
It doesn't matter,
as long as it quenches your thirst.

00:36:35.640 --> 00:36:37.120 line:80%
If Yan Zheng dares to say no,

00:36:37.120 --> 00:36:38.350 line:80%
I'll toss him out!

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:40.160 line:80%
If you had saved a donkey,

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:41.470 line:80%
it'd pull the millstone for you.

00:36:41.470 --> 00:36:42.390 line:80%
I'll talk to him if you don't.

00:36:42.390 --> 00:36:42.950 line:80%
Don't!

00:36:48.390 --> 00:36:49.720 line:80%
I'll talk to him myself.

00:37:09.560 --> 00:37:10.490 line:80%
Is something up?

00:37:11.950 --> 00:37:12.880 line:80%
Come in and talk.

00:37:25.120 --> 00:37:25.640 line:80%
I...

00:37:27.760 --> 00:37:28.830 line:80%
I'm wondering...

00:37:33.720 --> 00:37:35.830 line:80%
I'm wondering if I can do laundry for you!

00:37:35.830 --> 00:37:36.760 line:80%
But those are...

00:37:36.910 --> 00:37:37.840 line:80%
You're welcome!

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:43.160 line:80%
Those are clean clothes.

00:37:51.910 --> 00:37:53.840 line:80%
Where did these clothes come from?

00:37:54.080 --> 00:37:55.080 line:80%
I snatched them.

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:57.430 line:80%
I'm going to wash them.

00:37:58.640 --> 00:37:59.840 line:80%
Let me help, Changyu.

00:38:21.200 --> 00:38:21.930 line:80%
Here you are.

00:38:31.350 --> 00:38:32.470 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:38:35.510 --> 00:38:36.830 line:80%
Would you be my...

00:38:38.120 --> 00:38:39.320 line:80%
matrilocal husband?

00:38:41.080 --> 00:38:43.120 line:80%
When I recover and leave,

00:38:43.120 --> 00:38:44.280 line:80%
I'll pay you money.

00:38:46.680 --> 00:38:47.600 line:80%
But I don't want money.

00:38:47.600 --> 00:38:48.680 line:80%
I want you.

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:50.310 line:80%
If you refuse,

00:38:50.310 --> 00:38:51.240 line:80%
I'll beat you up!

00:38:55.160 --> 00:38:56.620 line:80%
Then you'd better kill me.

00:38:56.870 --> 00:38:59.600 line:80%
Or you'll have to pay extra
to get me medical help.

00:39:00.470 --> 00:39:01.160 line:80%
You...

00:39:01.800 --> 00:39:03.200 line:80%
Don't squeal, piggy.

00:39:03.910 --> 00:39:04.720 line:80%
Be serious.

00:39:05.910 --> 00:39:07.760 line:80%
You're now acting as Yan Zheng.

00:39:08.310 --> 00:39:09.120 line:80%
Focus.

00:39:13.950 --> 00:39:16.350 line:80%
Uncle didn't get the title deed yesterday.

00:39:17.350 --> 00:39:18.550 line:80%
He'll probably lodge

00:39:20.350 --> 00:39:22.750 line:80%
a complaint with the magistrate's office.

00:39:23.430 --> 00:39:25.080 line:80%
To keep this house,

00:39:25.990 --> 00:39:27.200 line:80%
my only option

00:39:28.990 --> 00:39:30.790 line:80%
is to find a matrilocal husband.

00:39:35.080 --> 00:39:36.210 line:80%
Mom and Dad are dead.

00:39:39.830 --> 00:39:41.960 line:80%
This house is the only thing they left.

00:39:43.430 --> 00:39:45.690 line:80%
I can't lose it.
It's not only for my sake,

00:39:47.640 --> 00:39:49.370 line:80%
but also for Changning's sake.

00:39:53.120 --> 00:39:55.780 line:80%
I'm not forcing you
to marry into the Fan family.

00:39:55.910 --> 00:39:57.080 line:80%
I'm just...

00:40:00.160 --> 00:40:01.080 line:80%
asking.

00:40:14.430 --> 00:40:16.830 line:80%
Dry weather!

00:40:17.800 --> 00:40:20.510 line:80%
Beware of fire!

00:40:21.310 --> 00:40:22.200 line:80%
Come in.

00:40:28.240 --> 00:40:29.870 line:80%
Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao are both asleep.

00:40:29.870 --> 00:40:32.070 line:80%
I was worried no one would serve you tea.

00:40:36.160 --> 00:40:37.350 line:80%
You'd easily get chilly
after losing blood.

00:40:37.350 --> 00:40:38.120 line:80%
That tea has turned cold.

00:40:38.120 --> 00:40:39.120 line:80%
Don't drink it.

00:40:39.680 --> 00:40:40.810 line:80%
I made you some soup.

00:40:41.830 --> 00:40:42.830 line:80%
Thank you.

00:40:54.080 --> 00:40:54.870 line:80%
This is...

00:40:55.760 --> 00:40:58.160 line:80%
Pork liver soup. It helps replenish blood.

00:41:01.350 --> 00:41:03.990 line:80%
One bucket of offal
was left from yesterday,

00:41:04.390 --> 00:41:06.250 line:80%
so I made this soup for you with it.

00:41:12.120 --> 00:41:12.950 line:80%
It's a bit hot.

00:41:13.600 --> 00:41:14.640 line:80%
I'll eat it later.

00:41:19.470 --> 00:41:21.430 line:80%
You hate offal, don't you?

00:41:23.350 --> 00:41:25.410 line:80%
You had only a few bites of the noodles

00:41:25.560 --> 00:41:27.420 line:80%
with pork intestines yesterday.

00:41:27.680 --> 00:41:30.210 line:80%
You also dislike this pork liver soup,
right?

00:41:35.080 --> 00:41:36.610 line:80%
I wouldn't say I dislike it.

00:41:37.160 --> 00:41:38.510 line:80%
I'm just...

00:41:39.640 --> 00:41:40.440 line:80%
not used to it.

00:41:43.910 --> 00:41:44.990 line:80%
But...

00:41:45.990 --> 00:41:48.120 line:80%
I'm not able to offer anything better.

00:41:50.120 --> 00:41:51.800 line:80%
Pork liver soup helps replenish blood.

00:41:51.800 --> 00:41:53.260 line:80%
It's good for your health.

00:41:53.740 --> 00:41:56.680 line:80%
Just pretend it's medicine and eat it.

00:42:01.280 --> 00:42:02.410 line:80%
I'll leave you to it.

00:42:06.160 --> 00:42:06.950 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:42:17.160 --> 00:42:18.220 line:80%
I'll do as you said.

00:42:20.080 --> 00:42:21.540 line:80%
Then eat it while it's hot.

00:42:22.200 --> 00:42:23.310 line:80%
No, I mean...

00:42:24.910 --> 00:42:26.120 line:80%
I agree to be...

00:42:26.830 --> 00:42:28.290 line:80%
your matrilocal husband.

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:50.390 line:80%
Great.

00:42:56.470 --> 00:42:57.640 line:80%
If you stay,

00:42:59.990 --> 00:43:01.080 line:80%
I'll feed you by butchering pigs.